article.headline: Morgan's 19 lead Texas State over Miami (OH) 75-65
article.description: — Tyler Morgan had 19 points in Texas State's 75-65 victory against Miami (OH) on Saturday.
article.linkText: Morgan's 19 lead Texas State over Miami (OH) 75-65
article.story: OXFORD, Ohio -- — Tyler Morgan had 19 points in Texas State's 75-65 victory against Miami (OH) on Saturday. Morgan added eight rebounds for the Bobcats (1-1). Kaden Gumbs scored 14 points while shooting 6 for 12, including 1 for 3 from beyond the arc. Brandon Love shot 5 of 11 from the field and 3 for 8 from the line to finish with 13 points. Darweshi Hunter led the way for the RedHawks (0-2) with 21 points. Jaquel Morris added 12 points, eight rebounds and two blocks for Miami (OH). Mekhi Cooper also put up 11 points. NEXT UP Texas State next plays Tuesday against Oklahoma on the road, and Miami (OH) will host Coppin State on Friday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
